creator: Various
description: LibriVox recording of Christmas Short Works Collection 2015. This year's Christmas collection of short stories, poems and non-fiction features readings in English, French, German and Romanian - Summary by Ruth Golding. Read in English by Maria Kasper; Beth Thomas; Crln Yldz Ksr; David Lawrence; Sarah Jennings; Son of the Exiles; Ed Humpal; Ruth Golding; Tony Addison; Claudia Salto; David Wales; BettyB; Greg Giordano; LisaRubio; Winston Tharp; Garth Burton. Read in French by Herman Roskams. Read in German by Julia Niedermaier; Herman Roskams. Read in Romanian by Livia F. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
subject: librivox; audiobooks;short stories; Christmas; poems; xmas
